# .gitignore — rust-yaml
#
# Kept deliberately lean: only patterns that apply to this Rust crate. Personal
# agent/editor tooling (.idea, .claude, docs/superpowers) is also covered by the
# user's global excludesfile; the IDE + OS entries below are duplicated here so
# the repo stays clean for every contributor and on CI (macOS / Linux / Windows).
#
# cargo-fuzz artifacts (target, corpus, artifacts, coverage) are ignored by
# fuzz/.gitignore, not here.

# ── Rust / Cargo ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
target/
**/*.rs.bk
*.orig
# Cargo.lock IS committed: it pins the dependency graph for reproducible builds
# across the stable/beta/nightly × {ubuntu,macos,windows} CI matrix.

# ── Coverage & profiling ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
lcov.info
*.profraw
*.profdata
# Flamegraph / perf artifacts — see docs/PROFILING.md
flamegraph*.svg
*.flamegraph.svg
perf.data
perf.data.old
cargo-flamegraph.trace/
*.stacks
*.dtrace.stacks
*.folded

# ── Project scratch ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/RELEASE_NOTES.md
/debug_*
/test_*
debug_*
test_*

# ── Editors & IDEs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
*.iml
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/launch.json
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── OS files ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# macOS
.DS_Store
._*
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
# Linux
.directory
.nfs*
.Trash-*
# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
*.lnk

# ── Misc ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.bak
*.tmp
.env
.env.local
